1
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:16,239
After half a year of planning,

2
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:20,120
I, Mu Jiuyun, can finally, as the Princess of Northern Di,

3
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:23,360
marry the Great Jin's Iron-Faced God of War, Mo Yu.

4
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:24,290
Lower the sedan!

5
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:35,880
Gu Licheng and his wife, who killed my beloved

6
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:38,080
and forced me off a cliff,

7
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:40,370
have now sought refuge under Mo Yu.

8
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,080
If I want revenge,

9
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,920
today is the perfect opportunity.

10
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,680
Greetings, God of War.

11
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,160
On our wedding day,

12
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,090
how dare you be so insolent!

13
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:20,970
How dare you!

14
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,760
I am a princess!

15
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,880
This is Great Jin,

16
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,039
not Northern Di.

17
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,480
There is no princess here,

18
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,280
only Mo Yu's woman.

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:30,960
Or,

20
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,640
a dead person.

21
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,720
Even if I die today,

22
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,840
I will kill you all.

23
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:48,320
Oh no. The effects of the pill are backfiring.

24
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,380
Gu Chengyu, Mu Jiuyun, you can't escape.

25
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:13,960
Hand over the Pill Canon, or you will definitely die today.

26
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,920
Ayu.

27
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,220
If you want the Pill Canon,

28
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,370
come down and get it.

29
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:40,040
Congratulations on surviving.

30
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,280
Please help me get revenge.

31
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,200
Divine Power Pill.

32
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,640
Have you ever heard of the Pill Canon?

33
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,760
Legend has it

34
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,920
that the recipes in the Pill Canon can make

35
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:58,120
pills that stimulate human potential.

36
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,760
Do you really have this divine item?

37
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,420
As long as you help me get revenge,

38
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,760
once it is done,

39
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,770
I will offer you the Elixir Manual.

40
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,320
A Yu.

41
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,570
There is a ready opportunity now to help you get revenge.

42
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,200
Follow me.

43
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,079
This is the daughter of the Beidi Queen.

44
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,720
I can turn you into her.

45
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,360
As far as I know,

46
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,560
Gu Licheng and his wife have pledged allegiance

47
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,680
to Mo Yu, the Iron-Faced God of War of Great Jin.

48
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,600
And she

49
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:44,400
is exactly the God of War Mo Yu's...

50
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,160
Fiancée.

51
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,079
After the face swap,

52
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:53,120
you will be the Princess of Beidi.

53
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,079
No.

54
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,560
As a foreign princess,

55
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:03,420
what grudge do you have against Gu Licheng and his wife?

56
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,880
Why did you kill them?

57
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,720
No reason.

58
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,600
They deserved to die.

59
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,890
If you don't want your hand ruined,

60
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,560
answer me quickly.

61
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,160
Even if I die,

62
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,720
I won't tell you.

63
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,250
You'd better behave yourself.

64
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:47,280
Don't mention my appearance to outsiders,

65
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,840
or else.

66
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,600
If you die,

67
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,920
you can't accomplish anything.

68
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,800
General.

69
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,920
Gu Licheng and his wife are asking to see you.

70
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,800
Got it.

71
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,360
Without my order,

72
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,520
the princess is not allowed to step out of the room.

73
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:25,760
Yes.

74
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,380
Bad guys really do live for a thousand years.

75
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,960
Yanyin Pill.

76
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,520
It can temporarily enhance one's hearing.

77
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,120
Greetings, General.

78
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,520
How is the position of the Minister of Revenue coming along?

79
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,440
General,

80
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,200
With the Gu family's wealth,

81
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,920
we could have, after the previous minister stepped down,

82
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,440
secured the position.

83
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,480
But now...

84
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,460
A competitor suddenly appeared.

85
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,280
Who?

86
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:07,800
The new Vice Minister of Revenue, Su Cheng.

87
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,200
With your Gu family's wealth,

88
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:13,560
if you can't even deal with a mere Vice Minister of Revenue,

89
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,080
what use are you to me?

90
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,080
Understood.

91
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,760
I will do my best to obtain financial power,

92
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:22,000
so the General can hold both military and financial power.

93
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,520
So Mo Yu is this ambitious.

94
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,160
What's next?

95
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,600
Rest assured, General.

96
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,860
We already have a plan.

97
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,040
Tonight,

98
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,320
on Su Cheng's way to the capital to take up his post,

99
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,000
we will set up an ambush to kill him.

100
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,240
Don't leave any loose ends.

101
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:36,880
Yes.

102
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,680
Princess.

103
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,330
Are you alright, Princess?

104
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:44,400
Are you worried about the princess,

105
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,520
or yourselves?

106
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,400
I am just curious.

107
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,560
My wife and I have no enmity with the princess.

108
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:56,040
Why would she try to kill us?

109
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,360
As long as you leave no survivors in your operations,

110
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:01,720
naturally no one will come seeking revenge.

111
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,080
Rest assured, General.

112
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,120
Tonight, in the woods on the outskirts of the city,

113
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,040
besides us,

114
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,960
No one can leave alive.

115
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,720
Gu Licheng, Mu Yujiao,

116
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,920
since you've done so much evil,

117
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,000
I will use your ambush

118
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,660
to take your miserable lives.

119
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,000
Hold on, Princess.

120
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,640
The general has ordered

121
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,640
that you cannot step out of the room.

122
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,520
What if I insist on leaving?

123
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,440
Then forgive our insolence.

124
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,280
Why are you here?

125
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,120
I received news that

126
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:36,280
Gu Licheng and his wife will ambush the new Minister of Revenue tonight.

127
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:38,800
I think this is a good opportunity for you to get revenge,

128
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,040
so I came.

129
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,440
But it seems you already know.

130
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:47,000
I've arranged a helper for you.

131
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,680
When you're in danger,

132
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,280
he will come to your rescue.

133
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:05,850
Bo Baorui

134
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,020
Zhong Xiaqiang

135
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,380
Zijian Qiangqipin

136
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:12,720
Quan Xuhang

137
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,380
Quan Xuhang

138
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:13,960
Quan Yulong

139
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,620
Quan Yulong

140
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,000
Licheng Lefei

141
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:16,800
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguang Jing

142
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,400
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguang Jing

143
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:20,840
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo
